    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Signed informed consent obtained from the patient or parent/guardian. Assent will be
             obtained from all minors 11 years of age and older.

          -  Carrying a diagnosis of eosinophilic gastrointestinal disease, eosinophilic
             inflammatory disease, or food allergy OR family member, or normal control
      </textblock>
